title: 10/01/21 DPS Hour 1 Rodney Harrison
itunes:title: 10/01/21 DPS Hour 1 Rodney Harrison
description:
In this hour of The Dan Patrick Show, Dan reacts to the Cincinnati Bengals' win over Jacksonville to keep the Jaguars without a win and to further extend Jacksonville head coach Urban Meyer's misery. Plus, "Football Night In America" analyst and two-time Super Bowl champion Rodney Harrison joins the program to preview what Tampa Bay quarterback Tom Brady may encounter in his first trip back to Foxborough in a different uniform.
